Package org.cfpm.factbaseExtension

Class Summary
FactBase This class implements the data type "fact base" that the factbase extension provides.
FactBaseAssert This class implements the "assert" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseAssertAll This class implements the "assert-all" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseCreate This class implements the "create" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseExists This class implements the "exists?" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseExtension This is the main class of the factbase extension.
FactBaseFromList This class implements the "from-list" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseGet This class implements the "get" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseMember This class implements the "member?" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseNOf This class implements the "n-of" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseOneOf This class implements the "one-of" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseRAssert This class implements the "r-assert" primitive for the factbase extension, which is a variant of assert (see FactBaseAssert).
FactBaseRetract This class implements the "retract" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseRetractAll This class implements the "retract-all" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseRetrieve This class implements the "retrieve" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseRetrieveTo This class implements the "retrieve-to" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseSize This class implements the "size" primitive for the factbase extension.
FactBaseToList This class implements the "to-list" primitive for the factbase extension.
Retrieval This class provides the necessary functionality for retrieval from a fact base.
